                <div className="bg-slate-900 p-10 rounded-[40px] text-white">
                   <h3 className="text-sm font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Visitor Intelligence</h3>
                   <p className="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">Most of your traffic originates from the <span className="text-blue-400 font-bold">Manzini Region (42%)</span> followed by <span className="text-indigo-400 font-bold">Hhohho (30%)</span>. Consider regional marketing efforts for Lubombo.</p>
                   <button className="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Download Full Data Pack</button>
